import React from 'react'
import {} from "./checkout-form.styles";
const CheckoutForm = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormInline>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label>Họ<Required>*</Required></Label>
          <Input name="fname"/>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup>
          <Label>Tên<Required>*</Required></Label>
          <Input name="lname"/>
        </FormGroup>
      </FormInline>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label>Quốc gia<Require>*</Require></Label>
        <Input name="country"/>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>       
        <Input name="address" placeholder="Đường, Phường/Xã, Quận/Huyện"/>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>       
        <Input name="address" placeholder=""/>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>       
        <Input name="apartment" placeholder="Số nhà"/>
      </FormGroup>
    </Form>
  )
}

export default CheckoutForm
